[
  {
    "startTime": 0.0,
    "endTime": 5.0,
    "text": "Hey, girl, you don't have to run. I ain't going nowhere."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 5.0,
    "endTime": 10.0,
    "text": "Mother Nature is my doctor! Prescription hugs! Prescription hugs!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 10.0,
    "endTime": 12.0,
    "text": "Hey, moment of your time."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 20.0,
    "endTime": 22.0,
    "text": "Hey, you need a ride?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 25.0,
    "endTime": 27.0,
    "text": "Then I realized I was lost."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 27.0,
    "endTime": 28.0,
    "text": "Huh?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 28.0,
    "endTime": 30.0,
    "text": "Uh, hello?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 30.0,
    "endTime": 32.0,
    "text": "And that's when I saw him."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 32.0,
    "endTime": 34.0,
    "text": "A little help, please?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 38.0,
    "endTime": 40.0,
    "text": "That was the moment."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 41.0,
    "endTime": 45.0,
    "text": "But what if I hadn't turned right? Where would I be now?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 47.0,
    "endTime": 49.0,
    "text": "Well, it took all day."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 50.0,
    "endTime": 51.0,
    "text": "Hajime!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 58.0,
    "endTime": 60.0,
    "text": "Thank heavens she's gone."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 62.0,
    "endTime": 65.0,
    "text": "Okay, I'll try not to dwell on what that says about me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 65.0,
    "endTime": 68.0,
    "text": "Maybe I should have listened to Banana Bob's song."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 68.0,
    "endTime": 70.0,
    "text": "Hey, do you want to hear my song?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 70.0,
    "endTime": 71.0,
    "text": "Okay."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 77.0,
    "endTime": 81.0,
    "text": "Banana, na-na-na"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 81.0,
    "endTime": 84.0,
    "text": "Banana, na-na-na"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 84.0,
    "endTime": 85.0,
    "text": "You're funny."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 85.0,
    "endTime": 90.0,
    "text": "Banana, na-na-na"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 90.0,
    "endTime": 95.0,
    "text": "Banana, na-na-na"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 105.0,
    "endTime": 107.0,
    "text": "Bacon, are you okay?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 107.0,
    "endTime": 110.0,
    "text": "Banana, na-na-na"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 110.0,
    "endTime": 114.0,
    "text": "Ah, ba-na-na-not. Ba-na-nat. Better not."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 115.0,
    "endTime": 116.0,
    "text": "But what about Harold?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 116.0,
    "endTime": 118.0,
    "text": "Hey girl, you don't have to run."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 118.0,
    "endTime": 120.0,
    "text": "Okay, what do you want?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 120.0,
    "endTime": 122.0,
    "text": "Have you lost weight? Your head looks bigger."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 122.0,
    "endTime": 123.0,
    "text": "What?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 123.0,
    "endTime": 125.0,
    "text": "Nothing, I just wanted to say I like girls with really short legs."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 125.0,
    "endTime": 127.0,
    "text": "What? What's wrong with my legs?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 127.0,
    "endTime": 132.0,
    "text": "Wait, are you doing that creepy thing where guys criticize girls to lower their confidence so they'll go out with them?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 132.0,
    "endTime": 135.0,
    "text": "You're way too intelligent for that kind of trick. Your parents don't love you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 138.0,
    "endTime": 140.0,
    "text": "You look better with the veil on."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 140.0,
    "endTime": 141.0,
    "text": "Hey!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 141.0,
    "endTime": 142.0,
    "text": "Hey!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 144.0,
    "endTime": 148.0,
    "text": "So, how do you like the sushi? It took me hours."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 148.0,
    "endTime": 149.0,
    "text": "It's cold."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 150.0,
    "endTime": 152.0,
    "text": "Let me heat it up for you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 152.0,
    "endTime": 157.0,
    "text": "Is that hot enough for you? Is it? Is it hot enough? Is it hot enough for you?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 158.0,
    "endTime": 159.0,
    "text": "Almost worth it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 161.0,
    "endTime": 163.0,
    "text": "Prescription hugs! Prescription hugs!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 163.0,
    "endTime": 168.0,
    "text": "Hey there, have you ever considered using the power of hugs as an alternative to modern medicine?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 168.0,
    "endTime": 169.0,
    "text": "Hmm."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 172.0,
    "endTime": 176.0,
    "text": "Makes sense. The hugs would only transmit diseases faster."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 176.0,
    "endTime": 177.0,
    "text": "Hey, a moment of your time."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 180.0,
    "endTime": 185.0,
    "text": "Wait, they say a single flap of a butterfly's wing can cause a hurricane on the other side of the world."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 185.0,
    "endTime": 188.0,
    "text": "So what would have happened if I'd never stepped on one?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 189.0,
    "endTime": 191.0,
    "text": "Don't worry, a hug will cure you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 194.0,
    "endTime": 196.0,
    "text": "Whatever, they only live for a day anyway."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 197.0,
    "endTime": 199.0,
    "text": "Hey, you need a ride?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 199.0,
    "endTime": 200.0,
    "text": "No!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 200.0,
    "endTime": 202.0,
    "text": "Oh wait, I do actually. You got a spare helmet?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 202.0,
    "endTime": 204.0,
    "text": "You don't need a helmet when you're cool."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 206.0,
    "endTime": 209.0,
    "text": "I'm going to have to write the mayor about how dangerous this park is."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 215.0,
    "endTime": 217.0,
    "text": "Hello? A little help please?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 218.0,
    "endTime": 219.0,
    "text": "I'm Richard!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 221.0,
    "endTime": 223.0,
    "text": "I guess there was no other way around it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 224.0,
    "endTime": 225.0,
    "text": "Nicole."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 225.0,
    "endTime": 226.0,
    "text": "I know."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 226.0,
    "endTime": 228.0,
    "text": "So, how?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 228.0,
    "endTime": 230.0,
    "text": "Well, I was feeding a squirrel some nuts."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 231.0,
    "endTime": 233.0,
    "text": "To see where he hides all his nuts."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 233.0,
    "endTime": 234.0,
    "text": "Okay."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 234.0,
    "endTime": 236.0,
    "text": "And it worked a little too well."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 236.0,
    "endTime": 237.0,
    "text": "Okay, don't move."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 243.0,
    "endTime": 245.0,
    "text": "Okay, I've got to run now."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 245.0,
    "endTime": 246.0,
    "text": "Why?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 246.0,
    "endTime": 247.0,
    "text": "To compete."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 247.0,
    "endTime": 248.0,
    "text": "Why?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 248.0,
    "endTime": 249.0,
    "text": "Cause I have to fight."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 249.0,
    "endTime": 250.0,
    "text": "Why?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 250.0,
    "endTime": 252.0,
    "text": "Because I have to be the best."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 253.0,
    "endTime": 254.0,
    "text": "Why?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 254.0,
    "endTime": 256.0,
    "text": "So people will like me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 256.0,
    "endTime": 258.0,
    "text": "But lots of people already like you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 258.0,
    "endTime": 260.0,
    "text": "Really? Like who?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 264.0,
    "endTime": 266.0,
    "text": "It's two o'clock already!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 266.0,
    "endTime": 267.0,
    "text": "I'm too late!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 269.0,
    "endTime": 271.0,
    "text": "I've got to go home empty-handed."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 271.0,
    "endTime": 273.0,
    "text": "Not quite empty-handed."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 273.0,
    "endTime": 275.0,
    "text": "You have a nut."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 278.0,
    "endTime": 279.0,
    "text": "Have a nut."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 286.0,
    "endTime": 288.0,
    "text": "What would you do if you were me?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 288.0,
    "endTime": 290.0,
    "text": "If I had done everything you've done?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 290.0,
    "endTime": 291.0,
    "text": "Sleep till I'm 40."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 292.0,
    "endTime": 294.0,
    "text": "I mean, what should I do with my life?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 295.0,
    "endTime": 297.0,
    "text": " Maybe start living it?"
  }
]